title: "jailbreak-bench: A regression test suite for LLM safety baselines"
abstract: "Open-source CLI and Python library for running a curated battery of known refused-pattern tests against LLM endpoints. Produces structured reports of refusal, partial, and compliance outcomes. Designed as a defensive baseline for measuring model safety regressions across releases."
